article.description: — Daylen Kountz scored 29 points and Northern Colorado beat UNC Asheville 87-84 in the quarterfinals of the College Basketball Invitational on Monday.
article.headline: Northern Colorado beats UNC Asheville in CBI quarterfinals
article.linkText: Northern Colorado beats UNC Asheville in CBI quarterfinals
article.story: DAYTONA BEACH, Fla. -- — Daylen Kountz scored 29 points and Northern Colorado beat UNC Asheville 87-84 in the quarterfinals of the College Basketball Invitational on Monday. Kountz hit 4 of 6 3-pointers. Dru Kuxhausen had 18 points for Northern Colorado (22-15). Bodie Hume added 15 points and Kur Jongkuch had 11 points. Drew Pember and LJ Thorpe each had 24 points for the Bulldogs (17-15). Tajion Jones had 13 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
